\textbf{CubeMars AK60-6 V3.0 KV80} actuators.
The shoulder motor ($q_1$) and elbow motor ($q_2$) are each connected to
a SocketCAN bus (\texttt{can1}) via the DSDTech SH-C30A adapter and
controlled through the \texttt{ak\_v3\_bus.py} / \texttt{AK\_V3\_CAN.py}
driver stack.

